{"tid":2224031,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"四大天王｜劉德華做CEO 郭富城任副總裁？ 出手解決大陸半導體晶片荒","createTime":"2020-09-30T08:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T08:57:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61d4207c84862b5a730f2c0afed59959f80fe54a","tid":2224031,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:45:51.000Z","msg":"美國政府制裁大陸公司，高科技產品被限制出口，高端半導體晶片成為重災區。有報道預計到明年初，大陸將會缺少晶片可用。大陸政府急切解決晶片荒，以舉國之力提供數以十億計補貼，鼓勵由國企到民企自主研發晶片，解燃眉之急。甘詞厚幣下研發晶片公司如雨後春筍。日前一間自稱是研究院的公司中，在其簡介網頁赫然發現有疑似香港四大天王的名字出現。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200930/HFDGB3U46BDJBER4RD6YA4SVSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200930%2FHFDGB3U46BDJBER4RD6YA4SVSY%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kymlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=020a41fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200930%2FHFDGB3U46BDJBER4RD6YA4SVSY%2F&h=6ac55788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200930/HFDGB3U46BDJBER4RD6YA4SVSY/</a>"},{"pid":"d789405c4f05a6975266ec220c9bf30a91c317fc","tid":2224031,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:47:51.000Z","msg":"會唔會同名"},{"pid":"1c7ce61f4e6a687bd81a7bb7b735e474022a96f4","tid":2224031,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"點解唔搵王<span class=\"xx-large\">晶</span>"},{"pid":"895f6a6aa0207653f6925268939e1a6bc2228f2e","tid":2224031,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kfa-gtS0WO0acI-XXFk7d-w9LxY=/611x371/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V2D2CSFAAJC3HGUMD5VO23DKQU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fkfa-gtS0WO0acI-XXFk7d-w9LxY%3D%2F611x371%2Ffilters%3Aquality